				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Player notice the tree that contains Kagha's letter from the Shadow Druids. They might find it by chance or know it was there.\r\n\r\nThe note that sends players here reads like this: [The marks crisscrossing the page don't look scribed so much as slashed.]<br><br>Kagha.<br><br>Swamp-docks. Tree. Meet me. Alone.<br><br>Olodan."
				}
